This section is for those users that have been given access to the Steam API for publishing your game to that platform. To be able to use these functions you must have been accepted onto Steam previously, either through a publisher or through the self publishing system, and have set up the Steam Preferences and the Steam Game Options correctly.
There are a great number of different functions related to the Steam API, and so we've split them up into the following sections to make it easier to navigate:
